    {
      "end": 72.4000015258789,
      "text": "When it's hard you don't demand from the other",
      "start": 68.9800033569336
    },
    {
      "end": 78.5199966430664,
      "text": "You don't remember the things that got you here",
      "start": 74.26000213623047
    },
    {
      "end": 90.0199966430664,
      "text": "And letting go to the wrong fear Lost in this nostalgic memory",
      "start": 80.0999984741211
    },
    {
      "end": 98.41999816894531,
      "text": "And fear that you take with you as You act like you finally caught up and lost",
      "start": 92.12000274658203
    },
    {
      "end": 102.45999908447266,
      "text": "this time And it's easier to blame",
      "start": 98.41999816894531
    },
    {
      "end": 108.63999938964844,
      "text": "It's easier to say that you're not the same The same to anyone",
      "start": 102.45999908447266
    },
    {
      "end": 114.73999786376953,
      "text": "So I'm glad you took your little cop and ride with me",
      "start": 110.12000274658203
    },
    {
      "end": 118.9800033569336,
      "text": "Never trusted me, never really ever really wanted me",
      "start": 114.73999786376953
    },
    {
      "end": 125,
      "text": "Just wanted the correlate of the mouthpiece To say that you're society and you had something",
      "start": 119.5
    },
    {
      "end": 129.74000549316406,
      "text": "like that So amazing when you give free styles to you",
      "start": 125
    },
    {
      "end": 134.82000732421875,
      "text": "and you're mine They had no way, they didn't see",
      "start": 129.74000549316406
    },
    {
      "end": 143.63999938964844,
      "text": "They didn't help, they didn't alleviate I'm just a one single serving friend",
      "start": 134.82000732421875
    },
    {
      "end": 154.83999633789062,
      "text": "Away from hating everything you do Hating everything you always do for you",
      "start": 143.63999938964844
    },
    {
      "end": 161.94000244140625,
      "text": "Including me Lost in this nostalgic memory",
      "start": 155.4199981689453
    },
    {
      "end": 169.83999633789062,
      "text": "Now you're just hating everything that Holds you down",
      "start": 164.82000732421875
    },
    {
      "end": 176.3800048828125,
      "text": "Even though you held me all the way Until I gave you my heart",
      "start": 169.83999633789062
    },
    {
      "end": 178.74000549316406,
      "text": "And now you've thrown it away",
      "start": 176.3800048828125
    }
